 also covered related stories such as the marriage of GB hockey team captain, Kate Walsh, to teammate Helen Richardson. They trusted BT to handle the story appropriately because of our commitment to women’s sport. </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="15" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">We aim, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">between the web, Clare’s show and our sport coverage, to be the foremost venue for women’s sport stories, exclusives and campaigns. We expect that the success </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">of our venture will lead to other outlets, newspaper and online, following us in making women’s s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">port more of a focus than it has ever been.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Reasons why participation in sport by women decreases</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="16" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">A bunch of East End kids</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> wor